WEBVTT

00:03:26.013 --> 00:03:34.290
I was absolutely physically
and emotionally broken.

00:03:34.290 --> 00:03:38.000
But I knew that in order to move forward,

00:03:38.000 --> 00:03:43.230
I had to let go of the old Amy

00:03:43.230 --> 00:03:49.020
and learn to embrace the new Amy.

00:03:49.020 --> 00:03:52.350
And that is when it dawned on me

00:03:52.350 --> 00:03:56.080
that I didn't have to be five-foot-five anymore.

00:03:56.080 --> 00:03:59.000
I could be as tall as I wanted!

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:04.680
(Laughter) (Applause)